ğŸ’¾ C â€“ Old-School Fun

ğŸ¤¯ Print ASCII art using casted chars:

for (int i = 65; i <= 90; i++) {
    printf("%c ", (char)i);  // A B C ... Z
}


ğŸ’¡ Convert string to hex manually:

