ğŸ§  Template-based casting:

ttemplate<typename T>
T convert(const std::string& str) {
    std::stringstream ss(str);
    T val;
    ss >> val;
    return val;
}


ğŸ§± C# â€“ Cool with LINQ & Casting

ğŸ§® Turn a string into ASCII codes:

